            "enlarge_text": false,
            "text": "<p><strong>CURATED BRANDS THAT SELL</strong></p><p>MAIZON is a carefully<strong> curated </strong>platform for <strong>selected </strong>modern fashion- and concept stores.</p><p>We help you source products that are not only beautiful - but proven to perform.</p><p>• Not just for a season<br/>• High sell-through potential<br/>• Low-risk starter orders</p><p>MAIZON <strong>connects </strong>you with a curated selection of emerging and established brands across beauty,<br/>lifestyle, accessories, living, wellbeing and jewellery.</p><p>Every brand is carefully chosen for its aesthetic, quality, and commercial potential - ensuring it fits seamlessly into contemporary fashion- and concept stores.</p><p><strong>WHY RETAILERS WORK WITH US</strong></p><p>• Carefully curated - no overwhelming assortments<br/>• Selected with real retail experience<br/>• Focus on products that actually sell<br/>• Personal support & tailored recommendations</p><p><strong>We don’t just present brands - we help you choose the right ones.</strong></p>"
